definitions.definition: The act of coupling or joining ; union ; conjunction .
Sexual procreation between a man and a woman or transfer of the sperm from male to female; usually applied to the mating process in nonhuman animals; coitus ; coition .

main_definition: ( countable ) The act of coupling or joining ; union ; conjunction .
secondary_definitions: ( uncountable ) Sexual procreation between a man and a woman or transfer of the sperm from male to female; usually applied to the mating process in nonhuman animals; coitus ; coition .
